text: @FedEx is it impossible to deliver things when they are scheduled to be?
@MarkPeriphery @WesHauch @FedEx Omfg.  FEDEX IS THE WORST.  I hate having to use them on shipments.

@FedEx I don’t know what the deal is in my area but if a package is scheduled to deliver Friday I can never ever count on it.  Most of the time it’s not delivered and it is extremely frustrating.  I’ll start paying extra for UPS
@FedEx another Friday.  Another  scheduled delivery failed.  So sick of my local fedex
@FedEx soooooo you guys going to deliver my package on time?

@FedEx paid to have a package overnighted, it went out yesterday and was scheduled to be delivered today.  Now it says Monday.  That is not the service I paid for.  I hate shipping with you, there’s ALWAYS an issue.

@ChaddisRadd Hi, this is Lakin. I do apologize for any frustration caused. I'd be happy to check on your shipment. Please DM your name, address, city, state, zip code, tracking number, phone number, and email address. https://t.co/7vnSkvqx3r

@FedExHelp can I get some help.  I overnighted a package Wednesday was supposed to show up Friday and didn’t.  It was rescheduled for Monday.  Then I contacted you guys and had it setup to deliver today.  It doesn’t look like that’s going to happen either.

@ChaddisRadd Hello Chad, my name is Rebecca.  I apologize for the inconvenience you have experienced and would be happy to check on your delivery. Please DM your address, tracking number, and phone number. 
Thank you.
